flowchart TD
    DR([DILG Reports]) --> Pick[Select report type<br/>Barangay Profile · CBMS · Peace & Order<br/>Assistance · Vulnerable Sector · Disaster Risk]
    Pick --> Compile[Compile figures live from Supabase<br/>residents · incidents · beneficiaries · zones]
    Compile --> PDF[Generate PDF with barangay letterhead]
    PDF --> Done([Return to Dashboard])

    DR --> Admin{Admin tools<br/>hidden from DILG rep}
    Admin -- Activity log --> AuditView[View audit_logs]
    Admin -- Database backup --> Backup[Export data backup]
    AuditView --> Done
    Backup --> Done
